title: Bracelet, mid-19th century
medium: Hair, gold, black and white enamel
creditline: Gift of the estate and in memory of Robert B. Noyes
description: Bracelet of brown-gray hair, elaborately braided, and clasp in three sections of gold, ornamented, on outer sections, with black enamel, on central, with black and white enamel in design of floral spray.
